      "content": "I hear how heavy and isolating this feeling of loss is, and it sounds incredibly exhausting to carry the obligation of existing without the spark you described. Please consider speaking with a mental health professional who specializes in trauma or existential sorrow, as they can offer a safe space to explore why this shift feels permanent rather than prescribing a medical solution. You deserve support to navigate this darkness without having to perform existence alone.",
      "source": "target",
